50|$|Other popular decor {{items are}} pillows made of vintage <b>barkcloth</b> fabric, vintage linens, {{chenille}} bedspreads, vintage chandeliers, and anything with roses in the design. It is a soft, relaxed, feminine, romantic style of decorating that looks comfortable and inviting.|$|E
50|$|There {{has been}} {{approximately}} 300 variable features determined in {{the steps that}} go into producing <b>barkcloth.</b> They include such elements as the cultivation or care of trees used for their bark; ways of getting at the desired bast layer.|$|E
